<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang='zh-TW'>
  <head>
    {{> head}}
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.0.3/dist/leaflet.css"
		  integrity="sha512-07I2e+7D8p6he1SIM+1twR5TIrhUQn9+I6yjqD53JQjFiMf8EtC93ty0/5vJTZGF8aAocvHYNEDJajGdNx1IsQ=="
			  crossorigin=""/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Leaflet.awesome-markers/2.0.2/leaflet.awesome-markers.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./dist/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
     <header class="header">
        <i class="fa fa-refresh fa-2x" onclick="resetView()"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-compass fa-2x" onclick="getLocation()"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-info fa-2x" onclick="toogleInfo()"></i>
      </div>
    </header>
      {{> header}}
      {{> start}}
      <div class="main-info">
        <table border="1" align="center" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0">
      <tbody>
      <tr align="center" style="background:#efefef;">
      <td><b>PM2.5濃度</b></td>
      <td><b>空污顏色</b></td>
      <td><b>說明</b></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>0-12</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="#7FB73A">綠色</td>
      <td>空氣品質良好，大家皆可正常戶外活動。</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>13-35</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="yellow">黃色</td>
      <td>空氣品質普通，敏感性族群應減少體力消耗，特別是戶外活動。</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>36-55</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="#F7931C">橘色</td>
      <td>空氣品質對敏感性族群不健康。</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>56-150</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="#F52305">紅色</td>
      <td>空氣品質不良，如任何人有不適，應考慮減少戶外活動。</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>151-250</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="#E062C8">紫色</td>
      <td>空氣品質非常不良，任何人需減少戶外活動。</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td>>250</td>
      <td class="color" align="center" bgcolor="#5F2828">棕色</td>
      <td>空氣品質屬有害，建議避免戶外活動</td>
      </tbody></table>
        </div>

      <div id="map"></div>
      <span class="st">採用美國空氣污染品質指標</span>
      <div class="note">
      <h5>
        <br/>
        資料來源：<a href="http://www.mep.gov.cn/">中华人民共和国环境保护部</a><br/>
          <span class="updateAt">更新時間：</span><br/>
          </h5>

      </div>

  {{> end}}
  <script src="https://d3js.org/queue.v1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://d3js.org/topojson.v1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.firebase.com/js/client/2.2.9/firebase.js"></script>
	<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.0.3/dist/leaflet.js"
  integrity="sha512-A7vV8IFfih/D732iSSKi20u/ooOfj/AGehOKq0f4vLT1Zr2Y+RX7C+w8A1gaSasGtRUZpF/NZgzSAu4/Gc41Lg=="
	  crossorigin=""></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Leaflet.awesome-markers/2.0.2/leaflet.awesome-markers.min.js"></script>
  <script src="./dist/map.js"></script>
  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
